---
const currentYear = 2025; // O puedes usar: new Date().getFullYear();

const links = [
  { name: "Inicio", href: "/" },
  { name: "Nuestros Expertos", href: "/#expertos" },
  { name: "Sobre Nosotros", href: "/about" },
];
---

<footer class="bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 pt-12 pb-8 mt-auto">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
        <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 tracking-tighter hover:text-indigo-500 transition-colors mb-2">
          Pro<span class="text-indigo-500">Team</span>.
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 max-w-xs">
          Conectando profesionales de alto nivel con clientes que buscan excelencia y calidad en sus servicios.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">Navegación</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-center md:text-left">
          {links.map((link) => (
            <li>
              <a 
                href={link.href} 
                class="text-base text-gray-500 hover:text-indigo-600 hover:pl-1 transition-all duration-200"
              >
                {link.name}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">Síguenos</h3>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a href="#" class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-gray-400 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:text-indigo-600 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="sr-only">Facebook</span>
